HEADWORD: Brownness
<hw>Brown"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The quality or state of being
brown.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Now like I brown (O lovely brown thy hair);⟦br⟧
Only in <qex>brownness</qex> beauty dwelleth there.</q>
<rj><qau>Drayton.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

